data.description: Welcome to this 4-bedroom, multi-level home, where ample space and a practical layout meet a fantastic opportunity for customization! This home proudly boasts brand new siding and a fresh, new roof to ensure durability and curb appeal. Fresh new cosmetics with professionally painted walls and brand new carpets! The naturally lit, eat-in kitchen and accessible dining area open to a generous backyard, waiting for your personal touch. Featuring a split-level living room, sizable master suite, two adaptable tiled bathrooms, and a lower-level family room, this property seamlessly blends functionality with potential. With a 2-car garage and structural enhancements, envision transforming this space into your beautifully personalized haven!
